M3 — Real-Time Market Data Streaming
Status: DONE
Completed: 2026-04-13
Verification:
  - libs/contracts/ws_messages.py: Added MARKET_DATA_UPDATE enum and WsMarketDataUpdate payload model
  - libs/contracts/interfaces/bar_stream_interface.py: BarStreamInterface ABC, BarCallback type alias
  - services/worker/streams/__init__.py: Package init
  - services/worker/streams/alpaca_bar_stream.py: Full AlpacaBarStream implementation
    - WebSocket auth via Alpaca key/secret, subscribe to "bars" channel
    - Candle normalization (Alpaca JSON → Candle contract, CandleInterval.M1)
    - Repository persistence via upsert_candles
    - Callback dispatch with error isolation per callback
    - Thread-safe: all shared state under threading.Lock (§0.6 compliant)
    - Exponential backoff reconnect: 1s → 2s → 4s → 8s → 16s max
    - Auth failure (code 402) → ExternalServiceError (fatal, no retry)
    - Diagnostics: connected, bars_received, last_bar_at, reconnect_count, errors, uptime_seconds
  - services/api/routes/ws_market_data.py: WebSocket /ws/market-data/{symbol} endpoint
    - JWT auth via query parameter (same pattern as ws_positions)
    - market_data_ws_manager (WebSocketConnectionManager keyed by symbol)
    - REST /ws/market-data/stats diagnostics endpoint
    - Symbol normalization to uppercase
  - services/api/main.py: ws_market_data router registered
  - tests/unit/test_alpaca_bar_stream.py: 36 tests
    - Bar parsing (7): valid, missing fields, uppercase, optional, zero volume
    - Callback dispatch (3): single, multiple, error isolation
    - Repository persistence (3): upsert, failure isolation, no-repo dispatch
    - Subscription (5): normalize, additive, empty ignore, unsubscribe, nonexistent
    - Diagnostics (4): initial, after bars, after subscribe, error count
    - Lifecycle (3): stop idempotent, start sets running, double-start raises
    - Message routing (5): bar, success auth, success connected, non-JSON, non-array
    - Error handling (4): auth 402 raises, non-auth error, on_error, on_close
    - Thread safety (2): concurrent bar processing, concurrent registration
  - tests/unit/test_ws_market_data.py: 8 tests
    - Auth (4): valid token, no token, invalid token, expired token
    - Lifecycle (2): connected message includes symbol, symbol normalized
    - Stats (2): empty stats, connection info
  - All 44 M3 tests passing, ruff lint clean

