  - Stateless service: pure computation, no DB dependencies
  - Kelly criterion: half-Kelly with 50% cap, negative → zero
  - ATR-based: risk_budget / (ATR × multiplier) with stop-loss calculation
  - Risk parity fallback to equal weight without ATR data
  - Risk gate cap enforcement across all methods
